title: Person of Interest - It's over [FINAL OF SEASON 5] (05x13)
author: POI - Best Of
comment: I really wish this show would come back or at least a spin off

It's just like Pilot, shaw didn't have a purpose anymore, so the machine hired her again, even the machine said that it hired her for who she is, and the episode ends with Shaw walking the same way John walks in Pilot, these little details!
What a sense of accomplishment they all must have felt! Everyone associated with this series delivered a gift to its fans and viewers each week. Nice to go out on top!

John's last name starts With (Tal) and ends in a(s). There is 2 maybe 3 letters left. I came up with (s) in the season 2 the episode where John steals the marshals badge. Joss ask an old serves friend to get John's record for her eyes only. The picture was in the way for his name, but it ended in a(s). Even though John did not know Joss knew about John she never condeemed him. In fact she respected him more.       Chirp
3:00 is the exact same shot as the end of the Pilot. A nice touch.
